item.description:
This Tuesday, March 26, NAAAP Boston is hosting a professional development event, featuring Jessica Kim, founder of BabbaCo (http://www.babbaco.com/), which is a monthly subscription box that provides educational toys and activities for children. Jessica is an award-winning, multi-million dollar entrepreneur, starting her first business during college. She will be speaking this Tuesday about her experiences with start-ups.

Many new and aspiring business leaders will be attending this event, so this will be a great opportunity to network, as well as learn from an incredibly successful business leader.

Tickets for this event are $10 each. To learn more about this event or register, click here: http://www.naaapboston.org/Events/Calendar/tabid/2304/vw/3/itemid/3175/d/20130326/Default.aspx
